    <item>
      <title>[바이낸스] 24시간 열려 있는 전통자산 선물 거래, Phemex TradFi가 의미하는 것</title>
      <link>https://blockdailynews.online/news/2026/02/2026-02-06-phemex-introduces-247-tradfi-futures-trading-with-0-fee-carn/</link>
